From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Andrzej Hajda <andrzej.hajda@intel.com>
Date: Thu, 7 Mar 2024 14:47:58 +0100
Subject: drm/xe/xe3p: disable EU thread hang on exception

Xe3p supports out-of-band exception reporting.
To enable it legacy mode (EU thread hang) should be disabled.

v2: use XE_RTP_END_VERSION_UNDEFINED instead of -1

v3: reworked to eudebug v3 (Maciej)

v4: removed the empty bracket at the end of engine_tunings (Maciej)

Signed-off-by: Maciej Patelczyk <maciej.patelczyk@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Andrzej Hajda <andrzej.hajda@intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Dominik Grzegorzek <dominik.grzegorzek@intel.com>
(backported from commit 865a5da9722d80aa8495cf4f893ed13afe4f7154 drm-tip-eudebug)
Signed-off-by: Pravalika Gurram <pravalika.gurram@intel.com>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/xe/regs/xe_gt_regs.h | 1 +
 drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_tuning.c       | 4 ++++
 2 files changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/regs/xe_gt_regs.h b/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/regs/xe_gt_regs.h
index 315f355e2..b762e2ff2 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/regs/xe_gt_regs.h
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/regs/xe_gt_regs.h
@@ -539,6 +539,7 @@
 #define   RES_CHK_SPR_DIS			REG_BIT(6)
 
 #define ROW_CHICKEN				XE_REG_MCR(0xe4f0, XE_REG_OPTION_MASKED)
+#define   CHICK_HANG_SEND_EXCEPTION		REG_BIT(15)
 #define   UGM_BACKUP_MODE			REG_BIT(13)
 #define   MDQ_ARBITRATION_MODE			REG_BIT(12)
 #define   STALL_DOP_GATING_DISABLE		REG_BIT(5)
diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_tuning.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_tuning.c
index 316f5e2b2..614a1a99f 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_tuning.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_tuning.c
@@ -123,6 +123,10 @@ static const struct xe_rtp_entry_sr engine_tunings[] = {
 			     GHWSP_CSB_REPORT_DIS,
 			     XE_RTP_ACTION_FLAG(ENGINE_BASE)))
 	},
+	{ XE_RTP_NAME("Tuning: disable EU thread hang on exception"),
+	  XE_RTP_RULES(GRAPHICS_VERSION_RANGE(3500, XE_RTP_END_VERSION_UNDEFINED)),
+	  XE_RTP_ACTIONS(CLR(ROW_CHICKEN, CHICK_HANG_SEND_EXCEPTION))
+	  },
 };
 
 static const struct xe_rtp_entry_sr lrc_tunings[] = {
